name: Hey Skeletons! Hands Off My Hot Dog!
name_original: Hey Skeletons! Hands Off My Hot Dog!
description:
You sit down in your favorite diner with your favorite meal; one steamin fresh hot dog. But something is wrong today. You notice a group of skeletons approach you.

"Hey man that hot dog looks pretty juicy." one says to you as they draw near.

"Its been ages since i slurped down a delicious dog" whispers another.


You get the distinct feeling that these skeletal rapscallions mean to liberate you from your waiting wiener. You steel yourself for a fight.


Click to slap those bony boys away from your prize.

Made for my Game a week project, though this one took a biiiiit longer than that. Also made for the 2016 Halloween Jam!

ALSO! Featuring music by my pal Dan! Link to his stuff coming as soon as he tells me where to link!
